#

Cilantro Lime Dressing

10 min
$3.5
120 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeVegan

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Condiment

Tags:

DressingSauceVeganFresh

Description

A zesty and fresh dressing perfect for salads, tacos, or grilled meats.

Ingredients

  • fresh cilantro: 1 cup, loosely packed
  • lime juice: 1/4 cup
  • olive oil: 1/2 cup
  • garlic clove: 1, minced
  • honey or agave syrup: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • pepper: to taste
